{"tid":2053551,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【抗暴之戰】警武裝升級！速龍本月可用胡椒彈JPX6手槍 醫生：令氣管收窄3分鐘攞命","createTime":"2020-06-06T11:15:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T19:17:35.000Z","uid":202425,"like":15,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"47022b4f3d5175016a1df7debeba2926595e4c90","tid":2053551,"uid":202425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T11:15:37.000Z","msg":"全文請瀏覽蘋果日報：<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/3ePN4aK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F3ePN4aK&d=bCxsXTpKmrqj5N4FYztdx4gmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=aad71673\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/3ePN4aK</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/acP8VkA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FacP8VkA.jpg&h=d68cb747&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最新引入的胡椒彈手槍，主要是由火藥引發的裝置，本身不受強風影響，噴射速度為每秒80米。每顆子彈含10毫升，包括藍色辣椒油樹脂等成份，影響人體的眼、鼻及呼吸系統，可瞬間造成暫時性失明、咳嗽、噁心及作嘔，估計大約在45分鐘後，當事人的症狀才會逐漸減退。<br />\n<br />\n張崑陽表示，已就瑞士賣胡椒彈手槍一事向當地政府查詢，惟有關當局表示沒有相關武器出售本港的紀錄，故懷疑屬其他國家轉口出售。據他了解，事件已引起當地傳媒及議員關注，有議員正計劃在議會內，向瑞士政府提出質詢。他呼籲各國要正視武器轉售的問題，避免出售予打壓人權的地方。"},{"pid":"0312646e1f1c410fa595aaab22b2ddb2570f38e5","tid":2053551,"uid":202425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T11:17:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc43f7f0998b58339d4291c044adbd95d9fbb111","tid":2053551,"uid":343361,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T11:17:46.000Z","msg":"啲稅去呢到<br />\n準備攬炒用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"718bfe3cc2414d1b2a7cb6f585956212fd872c8e","tid":2053551,"uid":1654,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T11:18:28.000Z","msg":"喇，我有哮喘底，信唔信我做george Floyd"},{"pid":"97adc19212934c236f735c76ea720f49ff7d1788","tid":2053551,"uid":202425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit